case_address_found_1: N of Sycamore Hgts, E of Cook Cyn at 3000 foot level
case_circumstances: Jane Doe #01-77 was found in the foothills north of Sycamore Heights residential area (east side of Cook Canyon, approximately 3000 foot level, Highland).  She was described as a White female adult between 30-55 year of age, 61" (5'1"), 120 lbs, black hair with slight gray, brown eyes, dark complexion.  She was clad in dark blue, short-sleeve denim jumpsuit, white bra, bright green underpants, white shoes "White Bond" (laces on the side, rather than front), and turquoise socks. Jewelry included yellow metal bracelet (left wrist), small turquoise earring (pierced, right), metal beret, a yellow metal watch, and a white metal chain necklace with "Maltese Crucifix."
